<item>
            <title>[LU-17029] add support for openEuler derived OSes</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17029</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current lustre.spec.in only matchs vendor for openEuler Linux.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But the openEuler derived OSes have a different vendor name, e.g.&#160; KylinOS&apos;s vendor name is Kylin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should match rpm macro &apos;openEuler&apos; in the spec for openEuler and its derived OSes a.k.a openEuler family OSes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
